wdi-DT.TDS.DPPG.GN.ZS.def: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term obligations of public debtors and long-term private obligations guaranteed by a public entity.
wdi-DT.TDS.DPPG.GN.ZS.name: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service
